    "In this way, we endow HistoGPT with visual and linguistic domain knowledge, which is critical for tackling the challenging problem of generating histopathology reports from entire WSIs.",
    "Similar to Flamingo 28, we freeze the parameters of all pre-trained modules during optimization to further reduce the computational cost and to avoid catastrophic forgetting of the inductive biases encoded in the learned weights.",
